Open Meeting Agenda

Thursday, April 20, 2006

10:00 a.m.

This page has been updated with audio files (.mp3) of each item of the agenda. The speaker icon following each item is a link to the sound file. For detailed help with playing these files on your computer visit the Audio Recordings page.
